Education is for life, not merely for a livelihood. As long as we are unmindful of this __(21)__, the __(22)__ of our educational curriculum as well as that of our __(23)__ and students is likely to remain __(24)__. It needs human beings who cannot be replaced by computers and __(25)__.

Answers: 21-truth, 22-quality, 23-teachers, 24-inadequate, 25-robots

**Example 3: Elephants Passage (Lecture 4)**
Elephants are seed __(21)__. Forests without __(22)__ have been observed to not have young __(23)__ at all. This is because __(24)__ species disperse seeds only through elephants. The animals are phenomenal at __(25)__ themselves to new ecological conditions.

Answers: 21-dispersers, 22-elephants, 23-saplings, 24-certain, 25-adapting

**Example 4: Hygiene Passage (Lecture 9)**
