## 🟡 MEDIUM PRIORITY - Days 6-7 (Focus 10% time)

### 9. SENTENCE IMPROVEMENT

**Common Error Types:**

**Type 1: Used to (past habit)**
❌ She uses to live in London
✅ She used to live in London

**Type 2: Ought to + V1**
❌ You ought apologize
✅ You ought to apologize

**Type 3: Would + V1**
❌ She will happy
✅ She would be happy

**Type 4: Had better/would rather + V1**
❌ I had few eggs (means some eggs - wrong context)
✅ I had **few** eggs (means almost none - need to buy)

**Type 5: Being (Participle)**
❌ Being a rainy day, we could not go out
✅ It being a rainy day, we could not go out

**Type 6: Gerund Possessive**
❌ He objected to **me** using calculator
✅ He objected to **my** using calculator

